  ('optometrist-moex-03506', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '稜鏡應用在驗度儀（lensometer）來測試鏡片的屈光強度，光線經過這稜鏡折射影像會是：', '["直接向頂點", "直接向基底", "先向基底再向頂點", "先向頂點再向基底"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b6894011d36", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fe75217f7a02", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03507', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於菲涅耳稜鏡（Fresnel prisms），下列何者錯誤？', '["不管需要改正的稜鏡屈光度為多少，其厚度都約為1.0 mm", "可以減輕第四對和第六對腦神經麻痺所造成的複視感覺", "可以幫助視野偏盲的病人，減輕其症狀", "唯一的缺點就是會增加光學像差"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b6894011d36", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fe75217f7a02", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03508', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一患者右眼如需要處方為+5.00 DS及2△稜鏡基底朝內，可以將鏡片中心位置如何調整來達到效果？', '["向外偏心4 mm", "向內偏心4 mm", "向外偏心0.4 mm", "向內偏心0.4 mm"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b6894011d36", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fe75217f7a02", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03509', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位患者眼鏡處方右眼遠視+4.00 DS，左眼遠視+1.00 DS。當其看近物時，雙眼視線均向下偏移8 mm， 同時向鼻側偏移2 mm，其最後的稜鏡效應，下列何者正確？', '["4.0△基底朝上；1.0△基底朝外", "2.4△基底朝上；1.0△基底朝外", "2.4△基底朝上；0.6△基底朝內", "4.0△基底朝上；0.6△基底朝內"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b6894011d36", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fe75217f7a02", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03510', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳小姐右眼戴上一個+2.00DS/-4.00DC×090鏡片，其中心點相對於瞳孔，有6.00 mm 顳側位移及2.00 mm 上側位移，她感受到的稜鏡度是多少？', '["1.2△基底朝外及0.4△基底朝上", "1.2△基底朝內及0.4△基底朝下", "1.2△基底朝內及0.4△基底朝上", "1.2△基底朝外及0.4△基底朝下"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b6894011d36", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fe75217f7a02", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
